body:
This is the RalexBot page.

Here, you can browse the code, submit an issue or request, or even learn how to make your own commands. 

If you want to browse the code, it is located [here](https://github.com/LordRalex/RalexBot).

If you want to read the wiki, that is located [here](https://github.com/LordRalex/RalexBot/wiki).

If you want to submit a ticket, look [here](https://github.com/LordRalex/RalexBot/issues).

If you want to read the javadocs, look [here]().

If you want to get working on a command, check [here](https://github.com/LordRalex/RalexBot/wiki/Creating-Commands) out first.
name: Ralexbot
tagline: My personal IRC bot, in Java, using the PircBotX lib
